### Test Case 1.6: Invalid submit - Missing taskId
POST {{agentBaseUrl}}/api/v1/agent/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskType": "JAVA_CLASS_NAME",
  "opsType": "SUBMIT",
  "executionClass": "top.ilovemyhome.dagtask.agent.execution.EchoExecution",
  "input": "{\"message\": \"No taskId\"}",
  "dealer": "scheduler-001"
}

> {%
